00:03:07.759 --> 00:03:09.360
Anong detalyadong plano ang mayroon ka doon!

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:20.280
Napakabilis mo talaga, Mr. Shen.

00:03:21.840 --> 00:03:23.159
Master Shang Xin, nagpaulan ka,

00:03:23.159 --> 00:03:24.240
sinusubukang i-frame si Dayao.

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:25.400
Hindi ka niya ginawang mali,

00:03:25.400 --> 00:03:26.759
kaya bakit hindi mo siya pinakawalan?

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:27.719
Mr. Shen.

00:03:27.720 --> 00:03:29.070
Ang mga tao at mga demonyo
ay mula sa magkaibang mundo.

00:03:29.080 --> 00:03:30.800
Sundin ang aking payo at magsisi.

00:03:31.120 --> 00:03:32.280
Kung hindi,

00:03:32.639 --> 00:03:34.240
